Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 00:27:28 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] AI-2091 G4 re-scope: remove dead pre-mutation CAS,
 re-scope property onto B1 delegate-only block

Remove the dead G4 pre-mutation CAS (assertMutationAgainstCurrentState) that
became unreachable after AI-2115 made issueUpdate mutations skip snapshot reuse.
The G4 property (no stale-snapshot foreign mutation commits) is now enforced
by B1's always-active delegate-only block in checkWorkflowRules.

Changes:
- Remove MutationCasInput, MutationCasDecision, assertMutationAgainstCurrentState
  from proxy.ts (dead code since AI-2115)
- Remove the G4 pre-mutation CAS runtime block (~70 lines) from handleProxyRequest
- Remove snapshotLoadedFromStore (write-only after CAS removal)
- Emit stale-snapshot-mutation-rejected (type: delegate-enforcement) from B1's
  delegate-only rejection path in handleProxyRequest
- Remove preMutationCAS from DispatchIntegrityGateKey and GATE_KEYS
- Remove preMutationCAS gate wiring from createApp() bootstrap
- Delete ai-2091-g4-cas-wiring.test.ts and ai-2091-cas-and-wiring.test.ts
  (tests for the now-removed CAS function)

All 3 B1 property tests pass (the RED test is now GREEN).
All 13 G1-G3 dispatch integrity tests pass (untouched).
